parameters: \TA[1]Oh, so it's just you here. What about Candy and Sherbet?
\TA[1]Oh, so those kids are working hard too.

\TA[1]But are you okay? The exams are coming up soon, aren't
they?

\TA[1]Well? I don't really know about that. And I don't intend to
worry about it either.

\TA[1]Strictly speaking, we are also ultimately beings from
another world. If you look at it from the perspective of the
society where Kei lives, we are like foreign objects, meow.

\TA[1]I'm really grateful that you're willing to help, and I
appreciate it. But if we intervene, it will become
troublesome in various ways, meow.

\TA[1]...Even if you forcefully make friends with magic, improve
your grades, in the end, nothing will remain in your hands,
right?

\TA[1]I hope you don't see us as such bad beings even if it's not
such a grand story, meow.

\TA[1]Didn't you just say with your own mouth that we are foreign
objects?

\TA[1]There's no rule that says you can't be happy just because
you're considered a foreign object, meow.
\TA[1]Is Kei really unhappy with their current life?
\TA[1](--Huh? It's not as assertive as I thought...?)

\TA[1](It was quite tough until recently... but lately, I've made
some friends and I've gotten used to the activities of
magical girls like in advertisements.)
\TA[1]Becoming famous... well, it's not all bad either.

\TA[1](...Could it be that I'm unexpectedly satisfied with my
current life...?)

\TA[1]N-No, well, it might have gotten better compared to before,
but middle school was really tough!

\TA[1]Of course, I'm not saying that we don't have any
responsibility. But there are also kids who are able to
balance being a magical girl and their everyday life.

\TA[1]To be honest, whether Kei had a bright student life even
without being a magical girl...
\TA[1]Huh!? If you say something like that, it'll be war!
\TA[1]Nyaah, please stop the Iron Claw... nya!
\TA[1]What, I-I'm not putting that much effort...

\TA[1]It's not that way, meow! Candy and Sorbet are in trouble,
meow!
\TA[1]Ugh...! I'll go right away, tell me the location!
